name: Luck 6x9 Poet, Painter, Musician May 11, 2021
description: Derek Michelin (born May 14, 1972), better known by his stage name Luck 6x9, is a French rapper, producer, poet, painter and author from Marseille Provence. He is a member of the groupClickhaze. His stage name comes from his jersey number in high school, which in turn came from Buffalo, New York rapper/producer Luck 6x9. https://www.instagram.com/evartology/
